  manualRoomIndex: -1
  startDelay: 0.5
  tasks:
  - taskName: Place Necklace
    instructionText: Locate the golden necklace hidden. Place it onto its dedicated
      place in central sarcophagus to begin the awakening ritual.
  - taskName: The Gateway Guardian
    instructionText: Find the gilded cat. Bring it to the central altar pedestal
      to clear the path forward.
  - taskName: Place Dagger
    instructionText: Search carefully to discover Tutankhamun's cosmic meteoric dagger.
      Place the blade safely on top of the central sarcophagus.
  - taskName: Place Pottery
    instructionText: Retrieve the ceremonial pottery vessel hidden. Secure it into
      the central sarcophagus to seal the tomb and complete your trial.
